whole life story.

614
00:41:22,013 --> 00:41:24,948
I like the doctor.
Well, so do I.

615
00:41:24,950 --> 00:41:27,150
I adore the doctor.
But by god, 50 pages?

616
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:39,629
Some books are
supposed to be long,
you know?

617
00:41:39,631 --> 00:41:42,866
Thank Christ
tolstoy never met you.

618
00:41:42,868 --> 00:41:45,101
We'd have that great novel
<i> war and nothing.</i>

619
00:41:56,881 --> 00:41:59,115
<i> To be a novelist,</i>
<i> you have to select.</i>

