for two years and the book's
only 100 pages shorter.

623
00:42:04,990 --> 00:42:08,691
Five goddamn seconds
of peace is all I ask!

624
00:42:08,693 --> 00:42:10,126
Can't you give me
five goddamn seconds?

625
00:42:10,128 --> 00:42:12,295
God damn!

626
00:42:12,297 --> 00:42:15,598
It's the tip of the iceberg,
