00:42:24,276 --> 00:42:28,578
Why are you playing
all dewy-eyed ingenue?

630
00:42:28,580 --> 00:42:31,548
Because I did not imagine,
even taking you at
your absolute worst,

631
00:42:31,550 --> 00:42:33,917
you could be so selfish.

632
00:42:33,919 --> 00:42:35,685
I can't turn my
back on the work.

633
00:42:35,687 --> 00:42:37,186
Aline!

634
00:42:37,188 --> 00:42:38,821
It's what I do.
It's my job.

635
00:42:38,823 --> 00:42:40,990
And this is my job.

636
00:42:40,992 --> 00:42:43,660
When will you ever learn
how much an opening
night means to me?

