00:42:43,662 --> 00:42:43,660
Is this all right?

638
00:42:46,230 --> 00:42:46,229
Yes, you look lovely.

639
00:42:46,231 --> 00:42:50,567
Could you please put
the scarf on your downstage
shoulder when you enter?

640
00:42:50,569 --> 00:42:52,001
Thank you.

641
00:42:52,003 --> 00:42:55,238
It's an important
night for me.
I need you here.

642
00:42:55,240 --> 00:42:58,308
