every single night
for the past two years.

644
00:43:02,147 --> 00:43:03,746
Do you have any
idea what it's like

645
00:43:03,748 --> 00:43:05,281
coming home to
an empty apartment
every night?

646
00:43:05,283 --> 00:43:07,717
