time to be at my side
and support me.

650
00:43:17,095 --> 00:43:19,629
You don't understand.
You don't understand.

651
00:43:19,631 --> 00:43:22,332
We are at a moment
of radical crisis
with my book!

652
00:43:22,334 --> 00:43:24,067
Stop it. Stop it!

653
00:43:24,069 --> 00:43:24,067
I've never known you
not to be at a point

