you up at 7:00.

661
00:43:44,122 --> 00:43:45,622
I won't be there.

662
00:43:51,862 --> 00:43:53,930
Make your choice, tom.

663
00:43:56,900 --> 00:43:58,001
Right now.

664
00:44:01,640 --> 00:44:03,172
There's no call
for this, honey.

665
00:44:06,010 --> 00:44:07,276
Right now.

666
00:44:18,188 --> 00:44:19,889
Look what you
have done to me.

667
00:44:46,316 --> 00:44:46,315
He's under
a lot of pressure.

668
00:44:46,317 --> 00:44:49,919
If we don't keep
going now, I don't know
what'll happen to him.

669
00:44:49,921 --> 00:44:50,953
You want
the big hamper?

670
00:44:50,955 --> 00:44:51,921
And the thermoses.

671
00:44:54,191 --> 00:44:56,292
Thanks.

672
00:44:56,294 --> 00:44:58,995
You have to think
what it's like for him.

