going to get
this time back.

682
00:45:18,817 --> 00:45:21,084
It's one damn vacation,
for Christ's sake!

683
00:45:26,323 --> 00:45:28,891
Louise, a writer like tom,
i get one in a lifetime.

684
00:45:30,961 --> 00:45:33,730
