00:45:43,140 --> 00:45:44,474
Wave to the girls.

687
00:45:46,243 --> 00:45:48,411
All right, ladies!

688
00:45:48,413 --> 00:45:50,279
Are you ready for
our great adventure?

689
00:45:53,016 --> 00:45:54,083
Close your door, darling.

690
00:46:11,769 --> 00:46:15,037
You gotta
stop worrying about
Louise so much,

691
00:46:15,039 --> 00:46:16,405
they'll be back
before you know it.

692
00:46:16,407 --> 00:46:17,540
Tom,
where are we going?

693
00:46:18,542 --> 00:46:21,244
Ah, you'll see.

694
00:46:21,246 --> 00:46:23,045
We're supposed
to be working.

695
00:46:24,548 --> 00:46:27,150
This is work.

696
00:46:27,152 --> 00:46:31,053
I decided you can
never appreciate
the music of my book,

697
00:46:31,055 --> 00:46:33,956
the tonality
and Cadence,

698
00:46:33,958 --> 00:46:37,994
without experiencing
the dark rhythms

699
00:46:37,996 --> 00:46:39,862
that inspire me.

700
00:47:11,995 --> 00:47:13,863
Bourbon!
In a big ol' tumbler.
You?

701
00:47:13,865 --> 00:47:15,932
Martini, please.
Very dry.

702
00:47:15,934 --> 00:47:17,233
He'll have a bourbon.

703
00:47:17,235 --> 00:47:18,367
You got it.

704
00:47:23,273 --> 00:47:25,107
You hear it, Max?

705
00:47:25,109 --> 00:47:27,143
I don't care much
for music.

706
00:47:29,913 --> 00:47:34,383
There's a savage indictment
of your grim, puritan soul.

707
00:47:36,854 --> 00:47:39,021
Come on!

708
00:47:39,023 --> 00:47:40,256
There must be
one song you like.

709
00:47:43,460 --> 00:47:45,394
<i> Flow gently, sweet afton.</i>

710
00:47:48,198 --> 00:47:51,567
I'm partial to
<i> flow gently, sweet afton.</i>

711
00:48:08,085 --> 00:48:09,018
You got it, sir.

712
00:48:13,557 --> 00:48:14,457
Two bourbons,
gentlemen.

713
00:48:17,261 --> 00:48:21,898
The whole thing about jazz
is that these fellas
are artists.

714
00:48:25,535 --> 00:48:28,571
They interpret the song,

715
00:48:28,573 --> 00:48:32,408
letting the music
pour on out,
riff upon riff,

716
00:48:32,410 --> 00:48:33,910
just like I do
with words.

717
00:48:35,412 --> 00:48:38,381
To hell with
standard forms.

718
00:48:38,383 --> 00:48:41,918
To hell with
flaubert and Henry James.

719
00:48:41,920 --> 00:48:43,953
Be original. Hmm?

