"can I write one
good sentence?"

1221
01:25:04,866 --> 01:25:09,236
How can you say that?
Don't you want
to be remembered?

1222
01:25:09,238 --> 01:25:11,171
<i> This side of paradise</i>
was just put out of print,

1223
01:25:11,173 --> 01:25:13,207
for the first time
in 18 years.

1224
01:25:13,209 --> 01:25:16,643
<i> Gatsby</i> will go next.
