01:28:21,397 --> 01:28:25,832
<i> "is touched by that</i>
<i> dark miracle of chance</i>

1277
01:28:25,834 --> 01:28:29,369
<i> "which makes new magic</i>
<i> in a dusty world.</i>

1278
01:28:29,371 --> 01:28:31,772
<i> "Each moment is the fruit</i>
<i> of 40,000 years.</i>

1279
01:28:33,441 --> 01:28:36,843
<i> "The minute-winning days,</i>
