1281
01:28:41,449 --> 01:28:44,551
<i> "And like a man</i>
<i> who is perishing</i>
<i> in the polar night,</i>

1282
01:28:44,553 --> 01:28:46,653
<i> "he thought of</i>
<i> the rich meadows</i>
<i> of his youth,</i>

1283
01:28:47,722 --> 01:28:49,923
<i> "the corn,</i>

1284
01:28:49,925 --> 01:28:51,058
<i> "the plum tree...</i>

1285
01:28:52,494 --> 01:28:55,095
<i> "...and ripe grain.</i>

1286
01:28:55,097 --> 01:28:56,396
<i> "Why here?</i>

1287
01:28:57,965 --> 01:28:58,765
<i> "O lost!"</i>

