01:29:31,833 --> 01:29:32,766
<i> Mr. Perkins,</i>
<i> you have a call.</i>

1289
01:29:33,634 --> 01:29:34,901
From tom's mother.

1290
01:29:38,539 --> 01:29:39,606
Mrs. wolfe?

1291
01:29:42,443 --> 01:29:44,111
Who even heard
of such a thing?

1292
01:29:45,513 --> 01:29:47,013
Tuberculosis
