1302
01:30:15,144 --> 01:30:18,078
Best place for it, they said.
Right here in Baltimore.

1303
01:30:22,083 --> 01:30:24,151
His father died in
this very hospital,

1304
01:30:25,753 --> 01:30:27,120
just along the hall.

1305
01:30:28,956 --> 01:30:31,158
It's like tom's whole life
is leading him,

1306
01:30:32,794 --> 01:30:32,959
like a river,
back to his father.

1307
01:30:38,466 --> 01:30:40,033
