01:35:43,738 --> 01:35:44,871
<i> Dear Max,</i>

1327
01:35:46,173 --> 01:35:48,508
<i> I've got a hunch.</i>

1328
01:35:48,510 --> 01:35:50,844
<i> And I wanted to write</i>
<i> these words to you.</i>

1329
01:35:52,747 --> 01:35:56,182
<i> I've made a long voyage</i>
