1330
01:35:56,184 --> 01:36:00,286
<i> and I've seen</i>
<i> the dark man very close.</i>

1331
01:36:00,288 --> 01:36:02,288
<i> And I don't think</i>
<i> I was too much</i>
<i> afraid of him.</i>

1332
01:36:04,759 --> 01:36:06,426
<i> But I want most</i>
<i> desperately to live.</i>

1333
01:36:08,262 --> 01:36:10,964
<i> I want to see you again.</i>

1334
01:36:10,966 --> 01:36:14,167
<i> For there is such</i>
<i> impossible anguish</i>
<i> and regret</i>

1335
01:36:14,169 --> 01:36:16,870
<i> for all I can</i>
<i> never say to you,</i>

1336
01:36:16,872 --> 01:36:18,538
<i> for all the work</i>
<i> I have to do.</i>

1337
01:36:20,474 --> 01:36:23,042
<i> I feel as if a great window</i>
<i> has been opened on life.</i>

1338
01:36:24,445 --> 01:36:26,880
<i> And if I come</i>
<i> through this,</i>

1339
01:36:26,882 --> 01:36:29,115
<i> I hope to god</i>
