01:36:29,117 --> 01:36:30,784
<i> and can live up to you.</i>

1341
01:36:32,286 --> 01:36:34,354
<i> But most of all,</i>

1342
01:36:34,356 --> 01:36:37,524
<i> I wanted to tell you,</i>
