1343
01:36:37,526 --> 01:36:40,126
<i> I shall always feel about you</i>

1344
01:36:40,128 --> 01:36:42,028
<i> the way I did</i>
<i> that November day</i>

1345
01:36:42,030 --> 01:36:43,563
<i> when you met me</i>
<i> at the boat</i>

1346
01:36:45,366 --> 01:36:48,201
<i> and we went on top</i>
<i> of the building</i>

1347
01:36:48,203 --> 01:36:52,205
<i> and all the strangeness</i>
<i> and the glory and the power</i>
<i> of life were below.</i>

1348
01:36:54,175 --> 01:36:55,341
<i> Yours always,</i>

1349
01:36:56,343 --> 01:36:57,410
<i> tom.</i>

